org.rcsb.mbt.glscene.StructureViewerImpl.vec
Class Vec3d

java.lang.Object
  org.rcsb.mbt.glscene.StructureViewerImpl.vec.Vec3d

public class Vec3d
extends java.lang.Object

Vec3f is simply a data container class for a 3-element vector. It is typically used by generic 3D applications which may or may not use Java3D as the rendering API. This enables applications to be written in an API-independant manner.
